flowRoot.flowPara: At the end of a round where a rider crossed the finish line, and after all subsequent rounds, unfinished riders add 1:00.
Between stages, each rider keeps half of their exhaustion cards (rounded up).
For each stage, the 1st, 2nd, & 3rd place finishers receive 3, 2, and 1 Tour Points (TP) respectively.
After the final stage, the riders with the 1st, 2nd, and 3rd lowest total times receive 3, 2, and 1 Tour Points (TP) respectively.
The first two finishers subtract an additional 0:10.
No slipstreaming after the finish line.
All riders who finish in an unbroken line get the same time as the leader of that pack.
Once across the line, riders subtract 0:10 for each space they reached past the finish line.
